name: Aurora Borealis ACEO Print Northern Light 10
description:
A Print of the original ACEO (Art Cards, Editions & Originals).

This is a part of my nightscape series. They are done in gouache.

Were you sound asleep when the magenta and violet hues greeted your star-filled sky?



Dimensions: 
6.4 x 8.9cm = 2.5 x 3.5"

Medium: Canon ChromaLife 100+ Inks on 225gsm "Somerset Enhanced Fine Art Archival Paper" from ST. Cuthberts Mill.

It is signed and dated at the back.

Packing: Packed in protective sleeve in envelope.

Shipping: Standard Mail via Singpost.
